/span><strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></span></strong></span></p>\n</li></ul>\n</li><li style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;font-weight: bold;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">eSIM: </span></strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">2 virtual SIM slots (no physical SIM slots) </span><strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></span></strong></span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding-inline-start: 48px;\"><li style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;font-weight: bold;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">US version eSIM listings fall under this picker</span><strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></span></strong></span></p>\n</li></ul>\n</li><li style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;font-weight: bold;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Physical SIM</span></strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><strong>:</strong> (1 physical + 1 virtual SIM slots) </span><strong><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><br></span></strong></span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding-inline-start: 48px;\"><li style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;font-weight: bold;text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">Global and Japan versions of physical SIM listings fall under this picker</span></span></p>\n</li></ul>\n</li></ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><img src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0aT000000PnqL&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EMaT00000I5Tob\" alt=\"\" width=\"445\" height=\"369\" style=\"display: block;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;\"></img></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"> </p>\n<h2 style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"><a id=\"H3\" target=\"_blank\"></a>3. Is there any after-sales process for the non-EU iPhones?</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;text-wrap-mode: wrap;\"></span></strong></span></h2>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Non-EU iPhones may have features or limitations that differ from EU versions. To address this, CCBM agents may issue commercial gestures for affected customers (see grid below). However, customers still have the right to return their phones within the 30-day cancellation period.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><em><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Note: For orders delivered between November 25–December 31, 2024, customers can cancel until January 31, 2025.</span></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Pricing Grid on non-EU iPhones customers’ requests:</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"> </p>\n<div align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"border: none;width: 79.6917%;height: 130.926px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 19.2012%;\"></col><col style=\"width: 49.616%;\"></col><col style=\"width: 15.5146%;\"></col><col style=\"width: 15.5146%;\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 48.7037px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">iPhone version</span></strong></span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Customer concern</span></strong></span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Commercial gesture </span></strong></span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Applicable period</span></strong></span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 48.7037px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">China/HK/Macau</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Differences in eSIM/WLAN/FaceTime Audio/Satellite Emergency Messages</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">20 €</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\"><br><p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Legal Warranty</span></p>\n</td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33.5185px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">US (dual-esim)</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Ordered physical SIM, but received dual eSIM</span></p>\n</td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"vertical-align: top;border: 1pt solid #000000;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-align: center;margin-top: 0pt;margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">10 €</span></p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>"
}